OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FPolice body-worn camera footage of the
OL,7,Fmoment armed police were called after
OL,8,Ftriple killer Valdo Calocane
OL,9,Fapproached the headquarters of MI5 has
OL,10,Fbeen shown at the Nottingham attacks
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police officers attended
OL,14,FThames House in Millbank, London,
OL,15,Fafter Calocane, who appeared "calm"
OL,16,Fand "compliant", had claimed to have
OL,17,Finformation about a case on May 31
OL,18,F2021.
OL,26,@wD@^OUwD@cO]xD@EOUxD@OO]
