OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FPolice officers involved in a number
OL,7,Fof different arrests of Valdo Calocane
OL,8,Fhave given evidence on the sixth day
OL,9,Fof the Nottingham Attacks Inquiry on
OL,10,FTuesday 3 March.
OL,12,FUniversity of Nottingham Students
OL,13,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,14,FKumar, both 19, and grandad Ian
OL,15,FCoates, 65, were stabbed to death by
OL,16,FCalocane, who then ran over Wayne
OL,17,FBirkett, Marcin Gawronski and Sharon
OL,18,FMiller with Mr Coates' van on June 13,
OL,19,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police officer PC Graham
OL,7,FFoster responded to a call made by MI5
OL,8,Fheadquarters, Thames House, after
OL,9,FCalocane asked to speak to someone on
OL,10,FMay 31, 2021.
OL,12,FThe Met officer was called to
OL,13,F"suspicious circumstances" after
OL,14,FCalocane stayed outside the building
OL,15,Fbut said it was not rare for people to
OL,16,Fbe outside protected locations.
OL,26,@uD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,F"It's not infrequent, it does occur,
OL,7,Fwhether it is outside Thames House or
OL,8,Fwhether it's actually outside other
OL,9,Fdiplomatic or protected or place of
OL,10,Finterest. It is not infrequent," PC
OL,11,FFoster told Rachel Langdale KC,
OL,12,Fcounsel for the Nottingham Inquiry.
OL,14,FOn Tuesday, the inquiry, which is
OL,15,Fbeing held in London, was shown
OL,16,Ffootage of Calocane wearing an all-
OL,17,Fblack outfit, including a hooded coat,
OL,18,Foutside the MI5 building despite it
OL,19,Fbeing described as a hot day.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard Calocane pressed the
OL,7,Fbuilding's intercom after arriving at
OL,8,Faround 5pm and told a member of MI5
OL,9,Fsecurity staff that he wanted to be
OL,10,Farrested.
OL,12,FPC Foster said Calocane had
OL,13,Fbeen"coherent" and "compliant" and had
OL,14,Fleft the MI5 headquarters after being
OL,15,Ftold he could not speak to someone, as
OL,16,Fit was a bank holiday, and had already
OL,17,Fbooked an Uber by the time officers
OL,18,Farrived.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@NO]uD@TOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,F"I had no concerns at that time for
OL,7,F(Calocane) or anybody else. I was
OL,8,Fhappy and content with the information
OL,9,Fhe provided to me and his demeanour.
OL,11,F"He was clear, concise, coherent and
OL,12,Fthat he had already booked an Uber
OL,13,Fbefore we attended the location. That
OL,14,Fhe understood and told me that the
OL,15,Fbuilding was closed due to a bank
OL,16,Fholiday and that he was going to go
OL,17,Fhome."
OL,26,@oD@ApmoD@JpnyD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FCalocane answered "not really" when
OL,7,Fasked if he had been arrested, but the
OL,8,FMet officer said this was not an
OL,9,Funusual response.
OL,11,FThe constable added: "It was for me, a
OL,12,Froutine stop. I work around protective
OL,13,Fsites and sites of interest. It was a
OL,14,Fvery routine stop and it didn't flag
OL,15,Fany concerns to myself."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@SOUnD@^O]sD@VOUwD@XO]
