OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FThe bodycam recording, played in the
OL,7,Finquiry's hearing room, shows him
OL,8,Fbeing questioned by an officer outside
OL,9,Fof MI5's headquarters.
OL,11,FOn Monday 2 March, the judge-led
OL,12,Finquiry heard evidence from five
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police officers who
OL,14,Fhad interacted with the paranoid
OL,15,Fschizophrenic back in 2020.
OL,17,FThe inquiry will also hear from
OL,18,FCalocane's former flatmate, Sebastian,
OL,19,Fwho lived with him between 2019 and
OL,20,F2020, and again when he returned to
OL,21,Fthe accommodation in 2021.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FSebastian, who is only giving his
OL,7,Ffirst name, will describe two
OL,8,Fincidents in July 2021 which caused
OL,9,Fhim to leave the accommodation.
OL,11,FThe first of the two incidents
OL,12,Foccurred on July 5, when Calocane
OL,13,Fgrabbed hold of him and forced him
OL,14,Fback against the wall.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FThe flatmate was also stalked by
OL,7,Fkiller Calocane in 2022. This was
OL,8,Ffirst publicly revealed by
OL,9,FNottinghamshire Live after a non-
OL,10,Fdisclosable police briefing. This
OL,11,Fbriefing is now the subject of an
OL,12,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1772572324
OL,3,CFootage of triple killer outside MI5
OL,4,CHQ shown to Nottingham attacks inquiry
OL,6,FOther witnesses due to speak today are
OL,7,FPC Foster and Supt Busby-McVey of the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police, who will talk
OL,9,Fabout Calocane travelling to MI5's
OL,10,Fheadquarters in Westminster and asking
OL,11,Fto be arrested on May 31, 2021. A
OL,12,Ffurther Nottinghamshire Police officer
OL,13,Fwill also be questioned.
OL,15,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,16,Findefinite hospital order in January
OL,17,F2024 after admitting manslaughter by
OL,18,Fdiminished responsibility and
OL,19,Fattempted murder, which has been
OL,20,Fcriticised by the victims' families.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
